---
import { NEGOCIO } from '../data/negocio';
---
<section id="por-que-elegirnos" class="reveal">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">¿Por qué elegirnos?</p>
    <h2 class="headline">Todo lo que necesitás,<br/>en un mismo <em>lugar</em>.</h2>
    <p class="lead">Capacidad para hasta {NEGOCIO.capacidad} personas. Un espacio pensado para que no tengas que resolver nada — nosotros ya lo resolvimos.</p>

    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-photo">
        <img src="/img/galeria/quincho-interior.jpg" alt="Quincho interno equipado" />
        <span class="tag">🏠 Quincho interno</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="amenity-list">
        <li><span class="amenity-icon">🏊</span><div><h4>Pileta 8×3 m</h4><p>Con solarium, deck y ducha exterior.</p></div></li>
        <li><span class="amenity-icon">🍽️</span><div><h4>Vajilla completa</h4><p>Pava eléctrica y cafetera de filtro, listas para usar.</p></div></li>
        <li><span class="amenity-icon">🔥</span><div><h4>Fogón recreativo</h4><p>Asador, asientos y mesada para la sobremesa.</p></div></li>
        <li><span class="amenity-icon">🌳</span><div><h4>Pérgola y parque</h4><p>Hamacas paraguayas, ping pong, metegol y espacio verde.</p></div></li>
        <li><span class="amenity-icon">♿</span><div><h4>Baño adaptado</h4><p>Con ducha, agua caliente y cambiador de pañales.</p></div></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section { padding: 96px 0; }
  .wrap { max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .22em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--madera-600); font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 12px;
  }
  .headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600;
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.6vw, 2.8rem);
    line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 14px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--madera-600); font-weight: 500; }
  .lead { color: rgba(15,31,25,.62); font-size: 1.02rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 46ch; margin: 0 0 0; }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px; align-items: center; margin-top: 52px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 900px) { .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .feature-photo {
    position: relative; border-radius: 22px;
    overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  }
  .feature-photo img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .feature-photo .tag {
    position: absolute; left: 18px; bottom: 18px;
    background: rgba(15,31,25,.75); color: var(--beige-50);
    font-size: .75rem; padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 999px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  .amenity-list { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .amenity-list li {
    display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 18px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15,31,25,.09);
  }
  .amenity-list li:first-child { padding-top: 0; }
  .amenity-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1; width: 34px; flex: none; text-align: center; }
  .amenity-list h4 { margin: 0 0 3px; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.02rem; }
  .amenity-list p { margin: 0; color: rgba(15,31,25,.58); font-size: .88rem; }

  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease; }
  .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
</style>

<script>
  const io = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('in'); });
  }, { threshold: 0.12 });
  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => io.observe(el));
</script>
